name: MetroCount Traffic Data File
summary: Learn about .EC0 files and view a list of programs that open them.

windows.name: Open over 400 file formats with File Viewer Plus.Free Download

content: EC0 raw data is created from a MetroCount Roadside Unit (RSU), which gathers time stamp data from air pulses that are triggered by tires that strike road axle sensors.

description: Data file used by MetroCount Traffic Executive, a program that generates traffic and vehicle classification reports for traffic surveys; contains report graphs, charts, and properties such as vehicle filter settings, units of measurement, colors, speed bins, classification schemes, and statistical settings.
